Addon.name: Flying Unicorn Addon
Addon.role: Have you always wished unicorns were in minecraft? Well with this addon it replaces horses with flying unicorns! It has different variants and when you ride them you can fly.

Addon.name: Unicorn
Addon.role: This add-on changes the average horse wandering around the world to give it a horn. which turns it into what? that's right a unicorn. these magical creatures act exactly like the horse you have in your stable but look a tad bit different to make them more unique.

Addon.name: Unicorns and Butterflies Add-on!!
Addon.role: And not just Unicorns and butterflies, there's Alacorns and Pegasus! Pegasuses?!? Pegasi?? Who knows!! They're horses that have wings! What else could possibly matter. AND they come in a crazy variety of colors. With sparkling things going everywhere. Make sure you wear sunglasses.

Addon.name: yFantasy
Addon.role: yFantasy is here! Bringing magnificent and dangerous resources to your exploration, you can hunt down dangerous vampires, tame baby dragons, trade wizards, meet several new biomes and much more!

Addon.name: 2 Seats on Horse v5 - Llama Update
Addon.role: Do you want to ride a horse with your friends? But you only have 1 horse. Don't worry, this Addon can solve your problem!. This addon allows you to ride a horse with 2 players. you can ride it as easily as you ride a boat. and also can be played on mobile, pc, and console versions. Made by Edsel.

Addon.name: Robot Horse Add-on
Addon.role: This add-on implements a four-legged mechanical horse to the game. It's much more powerful than an ordinary horse since it got the abilities to run faster, withstand more damage and jump higher. The robot revolution is finally here and the first to be replaced is a horse. Who would have known.

Addon.name: Candy Island Addon
Addon.role: Candy Island Addon is released! With it you can explore gigantic biomes completely made out of sweets! With over ten new structures, dungeons and more!

Addon.name: My Little Pony Addon
Addon.role: Are you looking for an addon with ponies, this addon can help you it adds ponies, unicorns, pegasus and alicorns, this addon will still have Updates with each one better than the other.
Addon.file_url: https://kossandroid.com/Data Android/Minecraft/Unicorn/14/MINE LITTLE PONY V4 OFFICIAL.mcaddon

Addon.name: Day of Dragons Add-on (Player Model) (1.14+ only)
Addon.role: The Day of Dragons Add-on will turn YOU into a 4D Dragon model with cool animations. It's like a dragon simulator which lets you become a cool dragon! Enjoy it!

Addon.name: Dark Dragon Addon
Addon.role: This add-on adds tamed and rideable winged dragons, these dark dragons have great strength and great speed in running and flying, and they protect you from monsters and help you in navigation and hunting. They are very wonderul !!

Addon.name: Dragon Brood
Addon.role: Do you want extra challenge to your survival world as you build yourself up to take on the Enderdragon?  The Enderdragon is willing to accommodate you!  She sends her Dragon Spawn Babies and her goons (or Dragoons) to pester you and just about any other mob around you. This Dragon Brood is pesky and can start spawning on you right after you spawn into your new world.

Addon.name: Aveo Dragon Addon
Addon.role: Too many dragons is not enough! We know that, you know that. Here's how we're helping: the Aveo Dragon. These long-necked, long-tailed, two-legged dragons of legend are here at last.

Addon.name: Aether Dragon Addon
Addon.role: Have you ever wanted a powerful pet aether dragon? If you do, then consider yourself lucky. I made it in Minecraft. This addon adds an Aether Dragon, one hostile, and one tamable. Be prepared though, it will be challenging to get a pet Aether Dragon.

Addon.name: Dragon Morph Addon
Addon.role: Ender Dragons are majestic creatures right? Wouldn't it be cool if you could become one. This addon makes it possible! Turning into one isn't going to be that easy though.

Addon.name: Curse Dragon
Addon.role: The curse Ender Dragon! It's just ender dragon but he's not look like normal ender dragon it has 3 heads and four wings And he can summon huge groups of lightning bolts!

Addon.name: Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Maid Addon (Unofficial)
Addon.role: Do you like Anime? This is a Minecraft recreation of one of Elon Musk's recommended animes.Summon a maid, transform it into a dragon and fly wth Tohru, Kanna, Elma, Lucoa! This add-on's based on 'Miss Kobayashi's Dragon Maid' by Coolkyousinnjya.

Addon.name: Dragon Ball Z Stands *NEW UPDATE*
Addon.role: My new dragon ball addon for minecraft mobile that adds stands like jojo's but dragon super that adds 9 characters in this version of the dragon ball addon.

Addon.name: Dragon Warboat
Addon.role: Be the Ruler of the Sea with your Dragon Warboat, and let loose with its Massive Crossbow. Mow down those mobs; you'll love it, they'll love it, everyone will love it.Shore bombardment anyone?

Map.name: Wizard101 Map (Revamped!)
Map.role: After losing a lot of my progress, I had to go back and re do but also add certain sections that made this this playable.  However, after your long wait, here is an update you have waited for.

Map.name: Horse Parkour [Parkour]
Map.role: This is a new take on parkour. Instead of running the parkour course yourself you will be riding a horse! It's slightly more difficult to control a horse than controlling the player (at least that's my opinion) and that makes this map quite hard actually. You can either play it in multiplayer or just play it by yourself.

Map.name: BETA Dragon Run
Map.role: This map is the minigame dragon run which I made the map for (check for proof on channel). However there are still many things & I need to improve & change so this is a warning!!! I’m not perfect if it doesn’t work I’ll try to fix it, but I’m not promising anything.

Map.name: Dragon Hunter House
Map.role: This is the Dragon Hunter House. A place where a hunter can settle for the night and plan for their next hunt.

Map.name: Kill Dragon [RPG]
Map.role: KILL DRAGON is an adventure map and RPG with more than 6 bosses to fight. Enchanted weapons and armor will be part of your equipment to enjoy the adventure.

Map.name: Ender Dragon Practice
Map.role: This map would help you improve/become more efficient at killing the dragon.This map is especially good for speed runners of if you just want to spend less time on killing the Ender Dragon in general.

Texture.name: Elytra Models
Texture.role: Want a more exciting elytra glider? These elytra models will change up your game. Either for roleplay toy story, being small, be part phantom or dragon. It's fun to change things up. Now added The Super Pack that adds in hero and villain style elytra models, and added 9 new elytra models. The Animals and Creatures Pack adds in 19 more elytra models where you turn into the animal or creature you choose.

Texture.name: Elves (R)
Texture.role: The Elves are coming to Minecraft World! They live in a tree house in the new magic biome along fairies, giant trees and unicorns. Discover this whimsical place and its secrets. Texture.role: For the first time ever, zombie horses can now be ridden in Minecraft Pocket Edition. Some things work a little bit different compared to a normal horse so make sure to read everything carefully!

Texture.name: Driveable Dragon Addon (0.17.0 Only!)
Texture.role: The ender dragon is being added as one of the new features in 0.17.0 of Minecraft Pocket Edition. This is an addon which makes it possible to ride and control the ender dragon.

Texture.name: UltimateEnderDragon Addon (1.0 Only!) (B)

Texture.name: Ender Horse Add-on (B)
Texture.role: This addon implements a new horse called the Ender Horse to the game. Its main feature is its ability to teleport. The teleportation is random so it's quite hard to control but it's nonetheless a quite unique feature for a horse. It has on average more health than other horses and it also has some boosted speed and jumping abilities.
